{
  "video_id": "I0TtovcwWno",
  "title": "A new way to mix oil and water",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6450.0,
      "end_time": 9190.0,
      "text": "Oil and water."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9190.0,
      "end_time": 10840.0,
      "text": "The reluctance of these two liquids"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10840.0,
      "end_time": 14200.0,
      "text": "to mix together and stay that way is so well known they"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14200.0,
      "end_time": 16419.0,
      "text": "have become cliche for any two things"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16420.0,
      "end_time": 19940.0,
      "text": "that do not go together well."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19940.0,
      "end_time": 22280.0,
      "text": "Currently, there are ways to mix the two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22280.0,
      "end_time": 26110.0,
      "text": "but ultimately, they will separate again."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26110.0,
      "end_time": 29600.0,
      "text": "So what if there was a way to not only mix oil and water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29600.0,
      "end_time": 30700.0,
      "text": "but to have the mixture remain stable"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30700.0,
      "end_time": 34720.0,
      "text": "for long periods of time, perhaps indefinitely?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34720.0,
      "end_time": 36970.0,
      "text": "Well, a team of researchers at MIT"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36970.0,
      "end_time": 40860.0,
      "text": "may have found a way to do just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40860.0,
      "end_time": 42540.0,
      "text": "Here we have oil and water represented"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42540.0,
      "end_time": 44580.0,
      "text": "by the colors red and blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44580.0,
      "end_time": 47220.0,
      "text": "Alone, these two liquids will not mix together."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47220.0,
      "end_time": 49500.0,
      "text": "But add in a soap-like substance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49500.0,
      "end_time": 52550.0,
      "text": "called a surfactant, then mix, and suddenly, the two liquids"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52550.0,
      "end_time": 54970.0,
      "text": "will blend."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54970.0,
      "end_time": 57220.0,
      "text": "This type of mixture of two or more liquids"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57220.0,
      "end_time": 59574.0,
      "text": "that are normally immiscible is called an emulsion."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62370.0,
      "end_time": 64690.0,
      "text": "Now, creating emulsions is not a new process."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64690.0,
      "end_time": 67179.0,
      "text": "Think of the mixture of oil and vinegar in salad dressings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67180.0,
      "end_time": 68170.0,
      "text": "for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68170.0,
      "end_time": 70000.0,
      "text": "But the challenge is to get the emulsions"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70000.0,
      "end_time": 74650.0,
      "text": "to remain stable for longer than a few minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74650.0,
      "end_time": 76810.0,
      "text": "The key to overcoming ultimate separation"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76810.0,
      "end_time": 81320.0,
      "text": "is to have really small, nano-sized droplets."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81320.0,
      "end_time": 84649.0,
      "text": "When the drops are that small, gravity cannot overcome them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84650.0,
      "end_time": 87780.0,
      "text": "and they can remain suspended indefinitely."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87780.0,
      "end_time": 89150.0,
      "text": "There are ways to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89150.0,
      "end_time": 91130.0,
      "text": "However, the current industrial processes"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91130.0,
      "end_time": 93979.0,
      "text": "are extremely energy intensive and expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 93980.0,
      "end_time": 96620.0,
      "text": "The new process used in the MIT lab"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96620.0,
      "end_time": 99770.0,
      "text": "requires very little energy, in fact, no mixing at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99770.0,
      "end_time": 103100.0,
      "text": "and can remain stable for months."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103100.0,
      "end_time": 105500.0,
      "text": "This new process takes a bottom-up approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105500.0,
      "end_time": 108560.0,
      "text": "by using condensation to create the droplets."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108560.0,
      "end_time": 112270.0,
      "text": "First, they take a reservoir of oil with an added surfactant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112270.0,
      "end_time": 114929.0,
      "text": "place it inside a chamber with very humid air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114930.0,
      "end_time": 116690.0,
      "text": "and cool the oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116690.0,
      "end_time": 118670.0,
      "text": "As it cools, the condensing water"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118670.0,
      "end_time": 120950.0,
      "text": "forms droplets at the surface that"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 120950.0,
      "end_time": 123830.0,
      "text": "spread through the oil-surfactant mixture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123830.0,
      "end_time": 126810.0,
      "text": "forming uniform, nanoscale droplets."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126810.0,
      "end_time": 129590.0,
      "text": "These droplets are so tiny and uniformed that they"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 129590.0,
      "end_time": 133649.0,
      "text": "are hard to even see under a microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133649.0,
      "end_time": 135190.0,
      "text": "The team believes the approach should"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135190.0,
      "end_time": 138220.0,
      "text": "work with a variety of oils and surfactants."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138220.0,
      "end_time": 141280.0,
      "text": "This new process could provide design guidelines for use"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 141280.0,
      "end_time": 142900.0,
      "text": "in particular applications that have"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 142900.0,
      "end_time": 146290.0,
      "text": "expiration dates, like drug delivery, cosmetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 146290.0,
      "end_time": 148560.0,
      "text": "and processed foods."
    }
  ]
}